🇧🇷🇺🇸 LIDE – Brazil Conference | Brazil Conference – New York, November 14 and 15, 2022 Location: Harvard Club

LIDE - Business Leaders Group will hold the BRAZIL CONFERENCE NEW YORK, on November 14 and 15, at Harvard Club, in New York (USA), to discuss The institutional and economic challenges of the elections in Brazil, with institutional support from the Brazilian-American Chamber of Commerce (BACC). Ministers of the Federal Supreme Court (STF), economists and businessmen are confirmed for the meeting, which will be moderated by columnist, political analyst and writer Merval Pereira.
